As of 9:49 AM PST on Wednesday, January 7, 2026, in Seattle, Washington, the weather is cloudy with a temperature of 41°F (5°C).

## Weather for Seattle, WA:
Current Conditions: Cloudy, 41°F (5°C)

Daily Forecast:
* Wednesday, January 7: Low: 34°F (1°C), High: 43°F (6°C), Description: Breezy with on-and-off rain and drizzle
* Thursday, January 8: Low: 41°F (5°C), High: 45°F (7°C), Description: Cloudy with a passing shower or two
* Friday, January 9: Low: 37°F (3°C), High: 52°F (11°C), Description: Cloudy
* Saturday, January 10: Low: 42°F (6°C), High: 51°F (11°C), Description: Mostly cloudy
* Sunday, January 11: Low: 44°F (7°C), High: 52°F (11°C), Description: Periods of rain and drizzle early in the morning; cloudy
* Monday, January 12: Low: 49°F (9°C), High: 56°F (13°C), Description: Occasional rain and drizzle
* Tuesday, January 13: Low: 46°F (8°C), High: 56°F (14°C), Description: Sun and areas of high clouds


January is Seattle's gloomiest month, with overcast or mostly cloudy skies about 71% of the time. ([axios.com](https://www.axios.com/local/seattle/2026/01/06/seattle-january-darkest-month-cloud-cover-sunlight-gloom?utm_source=openai)) The city typically experiences cool and wet conditions during this month, with average high temperatures around 45°F (7°C) and average low temperatures around 35°F (2°C). ([weather2visit.com](https://www.weather2visit.com/north-america/united-states/seattle-january.htm?utm_source=openai))

A Winter Weather Advisory was issued on January 6, 2026, for the Olympic Mountains, expecting snow accumulations of 6 to 12 inches and wind gusts up to 40 mph. ([govonestop.com](https://www.govonestop.com/alert/winter-weather-advisory-01062026-0751-washington?utm_source=openai))

Please exercise caution if traveling in the area, as conditions can change rapidly.
